config DAWN_OOT_DEMO_PROG
	bool "OOT demo: custom PROG classes"
	default n
	depends on DAWN
	---help---
	  Enable the demo's custom user-defined PROG classes (CProgMyEcho)
	  and the user PROG factory hook.
